    <text id="B0070T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Peter Hanger asks Jackson if he knows of anyone available for hire as a cook.
                    Hanger's letter describes the good working conditions in his home.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Mr T.P. Jackson</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-01-23"><abbr expan="January">Jan</abbr> 23<hi rend="super">d</hi> 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Waynesboro <abbr expan="Virginia">V<hi rend="super"
                            >a</hi></abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I wish to hire a good cook &amp; worker for my family <hi rend="underline">5</hi>
                    <hi rend="underline">Persons</hi>. For a good reliable woman I will give $6<hi
                        rend="underline">
                        <hi rend="super">00</hi>
                    </hi> Six Dollars per month the year round. I prefer hiring 12 at a time
                    everything is very convenient. Water is 10 steps of the kitchen &amp; the
                    wood always in the House. The <orig reg="labor">Labour</orig> is very light any
                        <orig reg="hearty">Harty</orig> woman can do the work with ease &amp;
                    not employed 2/3 of her time. if you know of such a One or one should call at
                    your office for hire let them know of the situation. I live in 1 mile of
                    Waynesboro depot. You will much oblige me by doing so.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Respectfully Yours</salute>
                    <signed>Peter Hanger <unclear>Jr.</unclear></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
